data.description: Beautifully maintained 3 bedroom 2 full bathroom ranch home on .4 acres!  This home has an updated kitchen with quartz counter tops and stainless steel appliances.  The outdoor area has a large deck and fully fenced in yard.  This home has a tankless hot water heater and smart thermostat.  The 2 secondary bedrooms have brand new carpet and the owner's bathroom has brand new luxury vinyl tile flooring.  This home is move in ready!
